<body>
    <h1>[OLD] Biometrics authentication on iOS and Android</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"7668cab7-1918-4329-830b-f6ad6de57ba5">
<style>[data-colorid=3Deppu9ejypt]{color:#6554c0} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Deppu9ejypt]{color:#503fab}[data-colorid=3Dxxcls0gvjv]{c=
olor:#6554c0} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dxxcls0gvjv]{colo=
r:#503fab}[data-colorid=3Dwj3vl9ejo3]{color:#6554c0} html[data-color-mode=
=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dwj3vl9ejo3]{color:#503fab}</style>In v3.23, we int=
roduce new feature to test biometrics authentication on iOS devices during =
manual session</p>
<p local-id=3D"67172ea7-93b7-42fb-9d99-106b394db324">In v3.24, we add suppo=
rt to test biometrics authentication in automation session</p>
<p local-id=3D"64cb5101-a385-4e04-8fc1-1b04194ed6e3"><span data-colorid=3D"=
wj3vl9ejo3">In v4.0, we add support to test biometrics authentication on An=
droid devices (for manual, automation and mixed session)</span></p>
<style type=3D"text/css">/*<![CDATA[*/
div.rbtoc1775440257143 {padding: 0px;}
div.rbtoc1775440257143 ul {list-style: disc;margin-left: 0px;}
div.rbtoc1775440257143 li {margin-left: 0px;padding-left: 0px;}

/*]]>*/</style>
<div class=3D"toc-macro rbtoc1775440257143">
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#id-[OLD]BiometricsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Preconditio=
n">Precondition</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#id-[OLD]BiometricsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Sendingbiom=
etricsauthenticationresponseinmanualsession">Sending biometrics authenticat=
ion response in manual session</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#id-[OLD]BiometricsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Sendingbiom=
etricsauthenticationresponseinautomationsession">Sending biometrics authent=
ication response in automation session</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#id-[OLD]BiometricsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-AdditionalN=
otes">Additional Notes</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"9faeefb3-c80f-47c4-808f-fe0c03a88c60" id=3D"id-[OLD]Biometr=
icsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Precondition"><span class=3D"inline-commen=
t-marker" data-ref=3D"972b0802-7c9b-425f-a56b-27d037803126">Precondition</s=
pan></h1>
<p local-id=3D"2cba9b9a-7dba-49e3-a70b-79246238f9d6">You need to alter your=
 application to use Kobiton custom library.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0fc30127-0d14-4545-8e1a-21e2280c9308">Refer to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9c481ab0-7928-43ab-83a6-b7ca4cf6bb4b">
<li local-id=3D"e5f4db24-28d9-463e-80fa-7af9a48d0f10">
<p local-id=3D"9aaabadb-1d59-4067-8218-8838c614b18a"><a href=3D"https://kob=
iton.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/KOBITON/pages/3452731437/iOS+-+Integration+w=
ith+user+application" data-linked-resource-id=3D"3452731437" data-linked-re=
source-version=3D"3" data-linked-resource-type=3D"page">iOS - Integration w=
ith user application</a> for how to integrate with iOS app</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a82b2209-6954-4002-b8e8-722f30a6f5c5">
<p local-id=3D"e46c5a7d-60aa-4508-9343-c38078425100"><a href=3D"https://kob=
iton.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/KOBITON/pages/3478749243/Android+-+Integrati=
on+with+user+application" data-linked-resource-id=3D"3478749243" data-linke=
d-resource-version=3D"4" data-linked-resource-type=3D"page">Android - Integ=
ration with user application</a> for how to integrate with Android app</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"be1945e1-6d72-4938-b6bc-372b4335b6a7"><em><span data-colorid=
=3D"xxcls0gvjv">(</span></em><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" =
data-account-id=3D"5ea7aa050590bb0b7bdf8c4d" href=3D"https://kobiton.atlass=
ian.net/wiki/people/5ea7aa050590bb0b7bdf8c4d?ref=3Dconfluence" target=3D"_b=
lank" data-base-url=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki">Dong Nhat Nguyen=
 (Deactivated)</a><em><span data-colorid=3D"eppu9ejypt"> <span class=3D"inl=
ine-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"19f9bb6b-57d0-477a-9771-90d83cc334f4">pleas=
e help to re-write this instruction</span>) </span></em></p>
<p local-id=3D"b1f458ee-70d7-40e0-bdec-6ef3db7c5fee">Once your application =
is ready, upload it to Kobiton App repo and use it in your test (manual/aut=
omation)</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"66c778f8-687f-423c-a2c1-7dd25bffaca4" id=3D"id-[OLD]Biometr=
icsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Sendingbiometricsauthenticationresponseinm=
anualsession">Sending biometrics authentication response in manual session<=
/h1>
<p local-id=3D"c55a33de-fbb4-400e-9a93-f51c2b4366d6">We added a new option =
on the left toolbar for biometric authentication:</p><span class=3D"conflue=
nce-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-s=
ize"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" width=3D"468" lo=
ading=3D"lazy" src=3D"7865e2589ffe46c67543aa9647993000a1d5d87eccd838dc4e092=
55af16f6691" data-image-src=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki/download/=
attachments/3451977744/image-20220824-013228.png?version=3D1&amp;modificati=
onDate=3D1661304752597&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"74=
3" data-width=3D"736" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resou=
rce-id=3D"3458924760" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resour=
ce-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220824=
-013228.png" data-base-url=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki" data-link=
ed-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D=
"3451977744" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"14" data-media-id=3D=
"88ba665e-eccf-42c3-8c8b-c692a6c6716b" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"4=
71"></span>
<p local-id=3D"b94e75c4-26e1-4b29-ab3e-613fdf500f61">When the application r=
equest for biometric authentication, Kobiton detects this request and promp=
t a dialog for you to choose a response. You can either choose Pass or Fail=
 response.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-=
wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-=
image image-center" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"223a71451aa3ebb79=
e8287c9df5be1395f240d4aabd5f97e68fdbf4d3e2ed581" data-image-src=3D"https://=
kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/3451977744/image-20220824-0=
13323.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1661304806419&amp;cacheVersion=
=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1426" data-width=3D"1462" data-unresolved=
-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"3459284993" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-re=
source-default-alias=3D"image-20220824-013323.png" data-base-url=3D"https:/=
/kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png=
" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"3451977744" data-linked-resource-con=
tainer-version=3D"14" data-media-id=3D"06c774fa-c4e3-4a78-9d93-20daa30b0f30=
" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"457"></span><span class=3D"confluence-=
embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"=
><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" width=3D"468" loadin=
g=3D"lazy" src=3D"7141624c27b87f1385167156089d5b4bf53f38ce5dacd97d62481f306=
4956df9" data-image-src=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki/download/atta=
chments/3451977744/image-20220824-013821.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDa=
te=3D1661305103866&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"320" d=
ata-width=3D"1386" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource=
-id=3D"3459153923" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-=
type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220824-01=
3821.png" data-base-url=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-=
resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"34=
51977744" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"14" data-media-id=3D"90=
1a2a97-5ef3-483e-9641-fb7662c11aa3" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"108"=
></span>
<p local-id=3D"7e4b355d-4a7d-4053-ade7-af8770745e07">There is a 20-second t=
ime-out, if you don't choose any response, after timed out, a Fail response=
 will be sent to the device</p>
<p local-id=3D"c3443202-48ca-41ac-aaef-14386e519f23">While the device is wa=
iting for your biometric authentication response, you won't be able to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"053f2045-d143-4a59-a5f4-02c11595da59">
<li local-id=3D"6c1ba655-1a0d-4e79-8f9e-aa14bfd8c690">
<p local-id=3D"491f7d39-f25f-4594-a8c6-3d3fa49bc53a">Touch/Type/Swipe on th=
e device</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39bfed72-e426-41e0-826d-5dfd5650ddc3">
<p local-id=3D"b2ad69ee-117c-48b8-83e6-7110415a913e">use these features on =
left toolbar: set timezone, location, sensitive data, image injection, mult=
i gesture</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e611dcad-aaa4-4245-8fae-1e14d75a7556">However, you will be a=
ble to use these features: adjust volume, click to return to Home screen, t=
urn off/on screen, rotate</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"07e58731-47c5-48bd-ad23-ee386767a750" id=3D"id-[OLD]Biometr=
icsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-Sendingbiometricsauthenticationresponseina=
utomationsession">Sending biometrics authentication response in automation =
session</h1>
<p local-id=3D"8c9a9008-4828-4db7-b4c5-1a0d33e4eaf5">This is newly added in=
 Kobiton version 3.24</p>
<p local-id=3D"2807691b-f869-4237-b130-a49a47b1bfe2">Use the following comm=
ands to trigger a successful or failed authentication in response to a biom=
etric prompt:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f0f09529-5478-4247-ac89-75ea2003472b">
<li local-id=3D"3bbf650f-b8a1-489c-b0a1-25cd7846287b">
<p local-id=3D"0efe67c9-74a1-4d20-a14d-bd09bc2896d9"><code>driver.execute('=
mobile:biometrics-authenticate', {result: 'passed'})</code> passes a succes=
sful authentication to the prompt.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2af3e8bb-7ff4-43a0-b068-56d4db689be3">
<p local-id=3D"56efd897-2dca-4560-8949-d289b2d44014"><code>driver.execute('=
mobile:biometrics-authenticate', {result: 'failed'})</code> passes a failed=
 authentication to the prompt.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0f4d439d-0215-442b-96c3-875bfcdc75bb">The following sample t=
est script show how to use the command:</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedd=
ed-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img =
class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" width=3D"468" loading=3D"l=
azy" src=3D"98f530c1bd34424b72b0b2c48a9f4b857efcb833976bd15e076d73152408a36=
3" data-image-src=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachment=
s/3451977744/image-20220929-085021.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1=
664441425162&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"245" data-wi=
dth=3D"768" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"=
3476553862" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D=
"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220929-085021.pn=
g" data-base-url=3D"https://kobiton.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resourc=
e-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"345197774=
4" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"14" data-media-id=3D"ee4565d0-=
9bc3-4f1e-b593-4cb291200c72" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"149"></span=
>
<h1 local-id=3D"df0d2b5a-e395-4518-8dc6-a1bce7007673" id=3D"id-[OLD]Biometr=
icsauthenticationoniOSandAndroid-AdditionalNotes">Additional Notes</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"66c22d4b-205c-4d7d-9a73-a851ca36ec19">
<li local-id=3D"ba35a655-6ff6-49cd-ae3f-1c3824983b59">
<p local-id=3D"4409a8ff-897c-452b-8016-538d09421152">This feature is only a=
vailable for Latest Kobiton devices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b81e664e-2056-41ae-81b2-6bd7aa28ff44">
<p local-id=3D"8cf99408-c5c6-47e1-9931-9090a76443cc">For iOS:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a4ea53c6-b251-46c7-871c-3cceaf3fee0c">
<li local-id=3D"2ef95e5e-ee05-4a93-910b-a2f614e2bd42">
<p local-id=3D"2c4d820d-3d1d-492c-8c99-55306ff1f7e3">Our custom library to =
support biometric authentication requires minimum iOS 11. Hence, if your de=
vices are in older iOS version, you won't be able to use this feature</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"c92ec501-043a-4afc-88ef-c9acd50a6285">
<p local-id=3D"7a04e667-64e4-4326-ab64-c97044b3cb9a">This feature is only a=
vailable for iPhone 5s and newer model</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"92f40999-91ba-40b2-bfa9-60283cce8847">
<p local-id=3D"0b188136-c4c3-4d06-b37a-afba72598781">For Android:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"964ff102-935e-438e-97cb-33b3380db348">
<li local-id=3D"d9a9604b-e681-462e-8497-7c5334fdbcc7">
<p local-id=3D"361c4f32-e451-4e87-9f74-46984088d8ca">We support:</p>
<p local-id=3D"661783b0-4773-4e6c-90de-c0971be6cfed">Official API<br><a cla=
ss=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://developer.android.com/reference/androi=
d/hardware/biometrics/BiometricPrompt#authenticate(android.os.CancellationS=
ignal,%20java.util.concurrent.Executor,%20android.hardware.biometrics.Biome=
tricPrompt.AuthenticationCallback)" rel=3D"nofollow">https://developer.andr=
oid.com/reference/android/hardware/biometrics/BiometricPrompt#authenticate(=
android.os.Cancel[=E2=80=A6]cPrompt.AuthenticationCallback)</a><br>
Androidx Biometric 3rd library<br><a class=3D"external-link" data-card-appe=
arance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://androidx.de/androidx/biometric/BiometricP=
rompt.html#authenticate(androidx.biometric.BiometricPrompt.PromptInfo)" loc=
al-id=3D"dfea657b-fe50-46af-b003-7ff545718c19" rel=3D"nofollow">https://and=
roidx.de/androidx/biometric/BiometricPrompt.html#authenticate(androidx.biom=
etric.BiometricPrompt.PromptInfo)</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7333354e-ff7b-4b67-b159-b9a64f763992">
<p local-id=3D"c8baec94-e8bf-4eb4-95c6-074c65ba9ec6">Not support: more secu=
rity with Crypto<br>
Official API<br><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://developer.androi=
d.com/reference/android/hardware/biometrics/BiometricPrompt#authenticate(an=
droid.hardware.biometrics.BiometricPrompt.CryptoObject,%20android.os.Cancel=
lationSignal,%20java.util.concurrent.Executor,%20android.hardware.biometric=
